modules.description: Handles progress tracking during file uploads by providing update and reset functions. Operates on integer counters and timestamped events to monitor transfer status. Used to display real-time upload progress in mobile applications.

Displays a progress indicator with customizable success and error callbacks, updates its message, and hides it, all using callback-based control flow. Operates with unit-returning functions and string messages. Used to manage user feedback during asynchronous operations in a Cordova-based application.
